          {
            "para_id": "art_2026-07-11_002_p9",
            "en_html": "<p>The European Central Bank asked 110 banks to present credible plans for dealing with the security threat from advanced AI models. The Bank of England also mentioned the threat from frontier AI in its latest report on financial stability, warning that the technology will “increase the sophistication and impact of cyber-attacks” on financial institutions and market infrastructure. Andrew Bailey, the Bank of England’s governor, called for co-operation among regulators in dealing with the security implications of AI, but said, unlike the ECB, he would not be issuing edicts to banks.</p>",
            "zh_text": "欧洲央行要求110家银行就应对先进AI模型的安全威胁提出可信方案。英格兰银行在其最新金融稳定报告中同样提及前沿AI带来的威胁，警告该技术将「提升针对金融机构及市场基础设施的网络攻击的复杂性与影响力」。英格兰银行行长安德鲁·贝利呼吁各国监管机构合作应对AI的安全影响，但他表示不会像欧洲央行那样向银行发布指令。"
          },
          {
            "para_id": "art_2026-07-11_002_p10",
            "en_html": "<p>Yields on Japan’s ten-year government bonds reached 2.9%, the highest since 1996, pushing up the costs of borrowing. Gross public debt is over 200% of GDP. As well as being concerned about the weak yen, investors are said to be worried about how the government is going to fund its recently announced $2.3trn, 14-year investment plan.</p>",
            "zh_text": "日本十年期国债收益率触及2.9%，创1996年以来新高，借贷成本随之攀升。日本公共债务总额已超过GDP的两倍。据称，投资者除了担忧日元疲软，还担心政府将如何为其近期公布的2.3万亿美元、为期14年的投资计划筹资。"
          },
          {
            "para_id": "art_2026-07-11_002_p11",
            "en_html": "<p>After holding out for a higher offer, easyJet, a European low-cost airline based in Britain, reached a preliminary agreement to be sold to Castlelake, an American investment firm, which would value the carrier at £5.5bn ($7.3bn). Castlelake, which has managed hundreds of planes through its leasing business, must make its offer official by August 3rd under British regulatory law.</p>",
            "zh_text": "在争取更高报价未果后，总部位于英国的欧洲廉价航空公司易捷航空与一家美国投资公司Castlelake达成初步收购协议，后者对该航空公司的估值为55亿英镑（73亿美元）。根据英国监管法规，通过飞机租赁业务管理着数百架飞机的Castlelake须于8月3日前正式提出收购要约。"
          },
          {
            "para_id": "art_2026-07-11_002_p12",
            "en_html": "<p>UniCredit, a big Italian bank, announced that it had increased its stake in Commerzbank, a German lender, to 47.6%. UniCredit has been trying to take over Commerzbank for over a year, but its overtures have been rejected by the German company and the German government.</p>",
            "zh_text": "意大利大型银行裕信银行宣布，已将其在德国商业银行——一家德国贷款机构——的持股比例提高至47.6%。裕信银行寻求收购德国商业银行已逾一年，但其收购意向一直遭到该德国公司及德国政府的拒绝。"
          },
          {
            "para_id": "art_2026-07-11_002_p13",
            "en_html": "<p>After declaring that the games industry is “facing the most severe hardware crisis in its history”, <a href=\"2550e315-ec21-480a-8a6f-3ca45a85b18d.html\">Microsoft cut 3,200 jobs at its Xbox business</a>, 1,600 of which were lost immediately. Profit margins at Xbox are lower than at its rivals and the wide availability of online gaming has eaten into demand for its consoles. It will also get rid of five of its gaming studios and reduce costs at Activision Blizzard, a games publisher it acquired in 2023 for $70bn.</p>",
            "zh_text": "在宣称游戏业正「面临史上最严重的硬件危机」之后，微软在其Xbox业务裁员3,200人，其中1,600人立即失去岗位。Xbox的利润率低于竞争对手，而在线游戏的普及侵蚀了其游戏机的需求。微软还将关闭旗下五家游戏工作室，并削减2023年以700亿美元收购的游戏发行商动视暴雪的成本。"
          },
          {
            "para_id": "art_2026-07-11_002_p14",
            "en_html": "<p>Sky, a European broadcaster, struck an agreement to buy ITV Media and Entertainment in a £1.6bn ($2.1bn) deal. ITV M&amp;E operates the network and streaming platforms of ITV, Britain’s legacy commercial channel. The transaction does not include the more lucrative ITV Studios, which produces ITV’s programmes, such as “Coronation Street” and “Poirot”. Sky is a subsidiary of Comcast, which intends to spin off Sky and NBCUniversal into a separate company.</p>",
            "zh_text": "欧洲广播公司天空卫视达成协议，以16亿英镑（21亿美元）收购ITV媒体与娱乐业务。ITV媒体与娱乐运营着英国老牌商业频道ITV的电视网和流媒体平台。该交易不包括利润更为丰厚的ITV影业，后者制作ITV的节目，如《加冕街》和《波洛》等。天空卫视是美国康卡斯特的子公司，而康卡斯特打算将天空卫视与NBC环球剥离，组建一家独立公司。"
          },
          {
            "para_id": "art_2026-07-11_002_p15",
            "en_html": "<p>This article was downloaded by <a class=\"producer_link\" href=\"https://z-lib.io\">zlibrary</a> from <a class=\"origin_link\" href=\"https://www.economist.com//the-world-this-week/2026/07/09/business\">https://www.economist.com//the-world-this-week/2026/07/09/business</a> </p>",
            "zh_text": "本文由zlibrary从https://www.economist.com//the-world-this-week/2026/07/09/business下载。"
          }
