            "en_html": "<p>A UKRAINIAN FLAG inscribed in Cyrillic with the words “Thanks, always” hangs at a factory in northern Sweden, where slabs of steel are transformed into hundreds of armoured vehicles each year. The flag was presented by Ukraine’s 21st Brigade, which operates the CV90 infantry fighting vehicle made here. Its soldiers affectionately call it “the Scandinavian beast”. The flag is a daily reminder to employees of how they are contributing to the security of Europe. “It is good to see that we have helped people,” says Julia, who works on an assembly line.</p>",
            "zh_text": "一面用西里尔字母题写着“永远的感谢”字样的乌克兰国旗，悬挂在瑞典北部的一家工厂里。那里，每年都有成百上千的钢板被改造成装甲车辆。这面国旗由乌克兰第21旅赠送，该旅装备的正是在此生产的CV90步兵战车。士兵们亲切地称它为“北欧巨兽”。对工厂员工而言，这面国旗每天都在提醒他们，自己正在为欧洲安全贡献力量。“看到我们帮到了人，很高兴”，在装配线上工作的朱莉娅说道。"
