            "en_html": "<p>This article was downloaded by <a class=\"producer_link\" href=\"https://z-lib.io\">zlibrary</a> from <a class=\"origin_link\" href=\"https://www.economist.com//britain/2026/07/09/theresa-may-britains-first-and-last-woke-prime-minister\">https://www.economist.com//britain/2026/07/09/theresa-may-britains-first-and-last-woke-prime-minister</a> </p>",
            "zh_text": "本文由 zlibrary 从以下网址下载: https://www.economist.com//britain/2026/07/09/theresa-may-britains-first-and-last-woke-prime-minister"
