            "en_html": "<p>This article was downloaded by <a class=\"producer_link\" href=\"https://z-lib.io\">zlibrary</a> from <a class=\"origin_link\" href=\"https://www.economist.com//international/2026/07/06/if-ludicrous-trump-flattery-can-save-nato-bring-it-on\">https://www.economist.com//international/2026/07/06/if-ludicrous-trump-flattery-can-save-nato-bring-it-on</a> </p>",
