            "para_id": "art_2026-07-11_058_p16",
            "en_html": "<p>This article was downloaded by <a class=\"producer_link\" href=\"https://z-lib.io\">zlibrary</a> from <a class=\"origin_link\" href=\"https://www.economist.com//finance-and-economics/2026/07/07/ai-has-taken-over-the-stock-market-the-bond-market-is-next\">https://www.economist.com//finance-and-economics/2026/07/07/ai-has-taken-over-the-stock-market-the-bond-market-is-next</a> </p>",
            "zh_text": "本文由zlibrary从https://www.economist.com//finance-and-economics/2026/07/07/ai-has-taken-over-the-stock-market-the-bond-market-is-next下载。"
