            "para_id": "art_2026-07-11_061_p5",
            "en_html": "<p>ON JUNE 28TH the Hlaitan, a tanker laden with liquefied natural gas, set off for France from Freeport, Texas. Almost immediately it changed course. TotalEnergies, its charterer, had received a better offer from Asia. According to Kpler, a data firm, the Hlaitan is due at its new destination on August 1st.</p>",
            "zh_text": "6月28日，满载液化天然气的“海莱坦号”油轮从得克萨斯州弗里波特启航驶向法国。几乎旋即改道。租船商道达尔能源收到了来自亚洲的更优报价。据数据公司Kpler称，“海莱坦号”预计于8月1日抵达新目的地。"
