            "en_html": "<p>This article was downloaded by <a class=\"producer_link\" href=\"https://z-lib.io\">zlibrary</a> from <a class=\"origin_link\" href=\"https://www.economist.com//culture/2026/07/07/why-old-master-paintings-are-back-in-vogue\">https://www.economist.com//culture/2026/07/07/why-old-master-paintings-are-back-in-vogue</a> </p>",
            "zh_text": "本文由 zlibrary 从 https://www.economist.com//culture/2026/07/07/why-old-master-paintings-are-back-in-vogue 下载。"
