            "en_html": "<p>For more on the latest books, films, TV shows, albums and controversies, sign up to <a href=\"https://www.economist.com/culture/2022/11/23/introducing-plot-twist-our-new-culture-newsletter\">Plot Twist</a>, our weekly subscriber-only newsletter</p>",
