            "en_html": "<p>This article was downloaded by <a class=\"producer_link\" href=\"https://z-lib.io\">zlibrary</a> from <a class=\"origin_link\" href=\"https://www.economist.com//culture/2026/07/09/the-real-value-of-the-bayeux-tapestry\">https://www.economist.com//culture/2026/07/09/the-real-value-of-the-bayeux-tapestry</a> </p>",
            "zh_text": "本文由 zlibrary 从 https://www.economist.com//culture/2026/07/09/the-real-value-of-the-bayeux-tapestry 下载。"
